org.ensor.algorithms.toposort

Interface INode<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of node that this graph represents.

    public interface INode<T>
    This interface implements a directed graph node by representing the node itself as well as any outgoing edges to the node. The remainder of the graph structure may be deduced by a simple collection of such nodes.
    Author:
    jona
